          "reference": "urn:uuid:11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
        },
        "payload": [
          {
            "contentString": "{patientName} was born at term without complications and has met all developmental milestones. He has a history of recurrent upper respiratory tract infections since starting kindergarten at age 3 [SNOMED:J20.9], typically two to three episodes per year. He has no prior hospitalizations and no known chronic pulmonary or cardiac conditions. He is fully vaccinated according to the Czech national immunization schedule, including annual influenza vaccination.\n\n{patientName} lives in a non-smoking household in a modern apartment in Brno. No pets are kept at home. He has no history of asthma or atopic dermatitis, though his mother has a history of seasonal allergic rhinitis. His diet is varied and age-appropriate. He attends kindergarten regularly and has had contact with other children exhibiting cold symptoms in the two weeks prior to this presentation [MEDLINEPLUS:J20.9]."
          }
        ]
      }
